name: Starliner launch
summary: Boeing's first planned crewed Starliner mission to the International Space Station has been postponed due to a technical issue. During pre-launch preparations, a valve on the Atlas 5 rocket's Centaur upper stage malfunctioned, prompting the launch to be scrubbed. The issue has prevented the spacecraft from reaching its intended orbit. Boeing and NASA are working to resolve the problem and determine a new launch date. This setback marks a delay in Boeing's efforts to demonstrate the Starliner's capabilities and join the ranks of spacecraft capable of transporting astronauts to and from space.

The pastor husband has been released and the church's website has been suspended amid the investigation. Meanwhile, memorials are being held in the community to remember Miller. The Robeson County Sheriff's Office is expected to release more findings in the case soon.

summary: Kim Kardashian elicited a mixed reaction at the "Greatest Roast of All Time" Netflix special honoring NFL legend Tom Brady. During her appearance, the reality star addressed persistent dating rumors linking her to Brady, both of whom have since denied any romantic involvement. Kardashian's presence drew both cheers and boos, with some audience members expressing their disapproval. She responded to the negative reaction with humor, jokingly comparing Brady to her recently estranged stepfather, Caitlyn Jenner. Despite the initial booing, Kardashian managed to win over the crowd with her self-deprecating and lighthearted performance, poking fun at the rumors and her personal life.
